Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.42,0:00:04.12,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A racing second hand, a shining comet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.12,0:00:07.49,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Conan's logic is good medicine\Nfor hearts tired by modern society!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.49,0:00:11.13,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The old guy goes on a date today!\NAll kinds of ripples are made!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.13,0:00:12.73,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.73,0:00:14.53,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.53,0:00:16.81,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
